name: MovieSurvey
0:
”alexa start movie survey”
”open movie survey”
”start movie survey”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie survey
des: This skill has been developed to get survey from the users of Alexa related to movies. whenever you will speak an invocation name or any testing phrase, a random question will be asked to you along with options. in response to that question you just need to speak any one from the given answer. If you say any other bogus word Alexa would not understand. to start again speak an invocation phrase.
